ideo/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A Note on Early Access</strong><br>As with any Early Access game, this is a work in progress. We will be adding so much over the coming weeks and months to the game, including tweaking the balance and quality of life as well as multiple content updates (more news on the fun stuff that is coming at a later date!). We will also, and most importantly, be listening to your feedback and fixing bugs and making the game the best it can be, together with your continued support. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770080/extras/64e8743fd5121ffbd3b580d748a9d2b0.avif?t=1760095997\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Please keep an eye on the Community hub for news, updates and patch notes. We are committed to building a game that will live up to the legacy of this genre we love.",
